content:
Create an Incident Channel

To route incidents to support agents via Omni-Channel:

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
Customize Application

In Setup, from the Quick Find box, enter Channels, and then select Service Channels.
Click New.
Enter a channel name and developer name.
Select Incident as the Salesforce object.
Set the capacity model to Tab-based.
Save your changes.
